signature_matches.name: check mutex
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: check mutex
    namespace: host-interaction/mutex
    authors:
      - moritz.raabe@mandiant.com
      - anushka.virgaonkar@mandiant.com
    scopes:
      static: basic block
      dynamic: thread
    mbc:
      - Process::Check Mutex [C0043]
    examples:
      - Practical Malware Analysis Lab 01-01.dll_:0x10001010
  features:
    - and:
      - or:
        - api: kernel32.OpenMutex
        - match: create mutex
        - api: System.Threading.Mutex::OpenExisting
        - api: System.Threading.Mutex::TryOpenExisting
      - optional:
        - or:
          - api: kernel32.GetLastError
          - number: 2 = ERROR_FILE_NOT_FOUND
          - number: 0xB7 = ERROR_ALREADY_EXISTS

signature_matches.name: allocate or change RWX memory
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: allocate or change RWX memory
    namespace: host-interaction/process/inject
    authors:
      - "@mr-tz"
    scopes:
      static: basic block
      dynamic: thread
    mbc:
      - Memory::Allocate Memory [C0007]

      # ntdll
      - 563653399B82CD443F120ECEFF836EA3678D4CF11D9B351BB737573C2D856299:0x140001ABA
  features:
    - and:
      - or:
        - match: allocate memory
        - match: change memory protection

        # lea     r9d, [rcx+40h]  ; flProtect
        # call    cs:VirtualAlloc
        - instruction:
          - mnemonic: lea
          - offset: 0x40 = PAGE_EXECUTE_READWRITE

signature_matches.name: link many functions at runtime

rule:
  meta:
    name: link many functions at runtime
    namespace: linking/runtime-linking
    authors:
      - moritz.raabe@mandiant.com
      - joakim@intezer.com
    scopes:
      static: function
      dynamic: thread
